No Flutter sdk configured.

comment_data.body:
Thanks for the report @xueyaodeai.  The plugin is not compatible with the 3.6 canary just yet but that's in the works (https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/pull/3527).

(Closing as a duplicate of #3522.)

title: Android Studio 3.6  plugin exception
